{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, it-- it got to the point where the SS were getting tired because they were-- they already-- they took all these young people and sent them to the front to fight the Russians because they were losing a lot of people then.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they-- they-- he told the SS, if-- if you are not gonna keep up, I'm gonna do the same thing to you-- shoot you like a dog.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We wound up from-- in Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gross-Rosen was a collector's camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was-- we-- we came to Gross-Rosen and we--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the march, however, to Gross-Rosen, the food was always a problem, so sometimes we would be able to find something because we always stopped where there was a farm, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I-- I remember, I found some eggs that-- and I brought-- an incident which is very important and I-- because we were like a group of seven, which we band together just to stay alive because we were marching with Cossacks, and we were marching with the gypsies, and we were marching with-- you-- you name-- you name it, with Poles.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is big bully, the Pollack, said to me, give me the eggs, I said no, I'm not going to give it to you, so he gave me a punch in the nose, and I was bleeding all over.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, one of-- we were like a group of seven-- one of the men, you know, he said, why do you pick on this little guy?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, he said, if you want to fight somebody, why don't you fight me?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, I'll be happy to fight you because it takes seven Jews to carry a bag of feathers, and you think you're going to whip me?",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
